{
  "stem": "24409.9",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was-- there was part of a staircase, which led to the outside, which was locked, and was not used.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there was a door-- I was living on a staircase.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But it was much better than a jail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there was [INAUDIBLE], and after two or three days, a monk came to me-- Father Richard Pliebel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Father Richard, who had been sent by the Irgun, who had somehow established-- there was a Jew with the name of [INAUDIBLE], who had connections with the Irgun, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But it had something with smuggling weapons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This [INAUDIBLE] probably did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But he was a [SPEAKING GERMAN] baptized Jew-- Catholic Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he worked for me, for to getting me a visa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was-- my passport had expired, in the meanwhile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he got me a visa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He was the-- he was the Father Confessor of the German Embassy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So they got the right man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And first of all, I got an extension of the visa by the German Embassy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And then he got me from a Catholic country, from Portugal, a visa, which was not a real visa from the consulate, but which he told me was arranged by somebody in a coffee house.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They arranged for the visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But he knew that this guy forges Portuguese visas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So I got a Portuguese visa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And now, with a Portuguese visa, and my British visa, I took a [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] fly ticket with with [INAUDIBLE] to Portugal, which was good.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was a very good country, very few refugees there, and was not forcing out refugees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I was, I didn't write about this in my book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I was horrified when we first come to Brindisi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "The plane landed, and they are still small planes at this time.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
